reviews.text: My friend and I had a set lunch each. We ordered clam spaghetti and mushroom pasta, got a soup or salad as the appetizer, with a drink each on the list. The food was great (Choices for vegan and vegetarian available). And the environment and service were pretty good too. Price was fair. Excellent experience. Will try again and recommend to others.
Taste good, need improvement in service.
decent food

今日下午去紅磡大都會逛街，看到這裡有間意粉狂熱，之前喺旺角吃過，便入去吃下午茶。
這裡的裝修比較時尚，座位都算寛敞。
Coffee caramel frozen $53，這個飲品未飲已經覺得很吸睛，因為高身的杯看上去，好有藝術感覺。咖啡味不算太濃郁，混合焦糖和忌廉之後，味道帶點甜，可以當甜品吃。
Cafe mocha$38，這個鮮奶比較多，不是我喜歡的味道，最後要女侍應，幫我加多些咖啡，之後味道變得更加好了。
香草烤雞凱撒沙律(大)$58，烤雞的雞肉，相當好味，而最重要是沙律醬，帶點芝士味，混合火箭菜之後味道很好。
帕爾馬火腿$48，火腿不會太乾身，而表面的橄欖油令到火腿的甘香充分發揮。
100%牛肉芝士番茄肉醬鮮制意粉$78，無論芝士、牛肉、蕃茄味都配合得天衣無縫，再加上煙煙靭靭的扁意粉，味道就更加一流，我非常推薦這個意粉。👍👍👍👍👍
法國焦糖布甸$38，厚厚的焦糖，覆蓋著凍的布甸，這個配合得很好，燉蛋不會太甜，味道適中，這個又是我喜歡的甜品。

演唱會日晚來食～未到7點已經要攞飛等位～
三文魚小食夾芝士～三文魚反而腥左～唔好食～
意粉係呢到主打～加10蚊意粉份量可以升級多半倍～
比拼過後～係多左粉既～但又多唔半倍咁多。。。
而pizza方面～見到有一人份量或二人份量～
一人份量真係好迷你～
整體不過不失～未到好好但叫唔差既選擇

result.name: Fortune Metropolis

reviews.text: Smaller shopping mall with more higher end Chinese cuisine dining options than normal. The mall is well-connected to Hung Hom station and allows you to pass through to the hotel area near the Hung Hom promenade at the back. Good shopping but no discussion experience of visiting here.

Fortune metropolis is a shopping  centre that acts as a hub for transport. It has a train station directly opposite as well as a bus terminus. It's also a short walk to the harbour and is close to several hotels. It contains many lovely restaurants and fast food as well.
I love this place because it's the least crowded of the malls around hung hom and whampoa.  it also has educational facilities which is a plus
A convenient shopping mall near the train station. But not have many shops.
Though variety of shops is limited but variety of food is great.
